// Criando a VLAN:

// O procedimento é o mesmo para cada VLAN..

    Interfaces > VLAN > Add

        New Interface
        
            General

                Name: VLAN10

                VLAN ID: 10

// Interface de saída para o outro mk (Tagged):
                
                Interface: eth2-mk2

// A mesma interface de saída/transporte pode ser usada para quantas VLANs desejar!

// Criar a VLAN nos dois mk, atentar a interface de saída!

// No mk1:

// Definindo o IP de cada interface VLAN:

    IP > Addresses

        Addresses List > Add

            New Address

                Address: 10.10.10.1/24

                Interface: VLAN10

                    IP > Addresses

// No mk2:

        Addresses List > Add

            New Address

                Address: 10.10.10.2/24

                Interface: VLAN10

// No mk1..

// Definindo os servidores dhcp para cada VLAN:

    IP > DHCP SERVER > DHCP Setup

// No mk2..

// Criar a bridge:

    Bridge > Bridge > Add

        General

            Name: bridge10

// Adicionando a interface Untagged e VLAN na bridge:

    Bridge > Ports > Add

        New Bridge Port

            Interface: eth1-pc10

            Bridge: bridge10

    Bridge > Ports > Add

        New Bridge Port

            Interface: VLAN10

            Bridge: bridge10

    Bridge > Ports > Add

        New Bridge Port

            Interface: eth2-pc20

            Bridge: bridge20

    Bridge > Ports > Add

        New Bridge Port

            Interface: VLAN20

            Bridge: bridge20
